data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Motivated Sellers!!!    Looking for an ideal home at an affordable price in a prime location? Look no further! This meticulously maintained residence is poised for its next owner. The charming property boasts a well-thought-out design, featuring three spacious bedrooms, two bathrooms, inside laundry, and a generous kitchen complemented by a welcoming living room. Nestled on a large corner lot within a quiet cul-de-sac, this cozy abode includes solid wood cabinets, ample counter space, a large breakfast bar adorned with a stone veneer finish, and a sizable pantry. The kitchen also opens up to the backyard/patio through sliding doors.    Notably, this home comes equipped with a built-in gun safe, adding an extra layer of security. As you explore the main hall, you'll discover a convenient laundry area tucked just off the kitchen. The expansive main bedroom is sure to impress, along with its well-appointed main bathroom. The guest bedrooms offer plenty of closet space and abundant natural light.    The two-car garage features a garage door opener, finished epoxy flooring, a workbench, and attic access. To sweeten the deal,  Benefitting from recent upgrades, this home now features a brand-new roof and stylish vinyl fencing, enhancing both its aesthetic appeal and structural integrity.  These thoughtful enhancements contribute to the overall value and desirability of this already well-maintained property.     This property qualifies for 100% financing through a USDA or VA loan. Situated in North Mulberry, right off Shepherd Road, it ensures quick access to Lakeland,  and I-4. The location is close to various amenities, including Publix, Lakeside Village, restaurants, salons, and more. Enjoy the well-kept, friendly neighborhood with nearby walking trails and numerous small ponds. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your home
